description: Deletes the practice run configuration for a resource. Before you can delete a practice run configuration for a resource., you must disable zonal autoshift for the resource. Practice runs must be configured for zonal autoshift to be enabled.

parameters.name: resourceIdentifier
parameters.description: The identifier for the resource that you want to delete the practice run configuration for. The identifier is the Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the resource.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the resource that you deleted the practice run for.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the resource that you deleted the practice run for.

nested_items.name: zonalAutoshiftStatus
nested_items.description: The status of zonal autoshift for the resource.
